# All `@widget-lab/*` packages would normally come from the private 3DS
# GitLab registry below — but reaching it requires Reporter access on
# the `widget-lab` group on itgit.dsone.3ds.com. To unblock builds,
# `@widget-lab/3ddashboard-utils` is currently sourced via a `file:`
# dependency in package.json (the source repo cloned into
# `<worktree>/.kw-pipeline/3ddashboard-utils`). If a contributor gains
# group access they can swap the dep back to a registry version and
# uncomment the line below.
#
# @widget-lab:registry=https://itgit.dsone.3ds.com/api/v4/packages/npm/
